American rapper and singer Faheem Rasheed Najm famously known as T-Pain has come out to apologised to those he ignored their messages sent to his inbox about two years ago. The music star shared a video of his DM where renowned international celebrities and some Nigerian celebrities have been trying to reach him via his Instagram inbox for about two years. Nigerian celebrities like DJ cuppy, Mayorkun and Ghanian /Nigerian celebrity Juliet Ibrahim profiles also appeared in the video. Juliet Ibrahim is trending on Twitter for sending a message “Hi ya”, to the music star. T-Pain wrote: “I thought DM’s are supposed to just show up in the normal folder and you do not have to go digging for all these”, he explained via typing. “I apologise to everybody on this list and hundreds of others I couldn’t fit in this video,” he wrote